  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我想画一个Git流程图，展示从分支向上cherry-pick的典型场景。标题就叫「Cherry-pick from branch (bottom-to-top)」吧，方向是从下往上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "gitGraph BT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，从下往上布局。我先在main分支上创建一个初始commit，然后分出新分支newbranch，这样结构对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "newbranch",
        "commit",
        "branch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，然后在newbranch上做一个标记为「Pick me」的commit，这个commit后面要被cherry-pick回main。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "newbranch",
        "commit id: \"Pick me\""
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我切回main分支再加一个commit，然后再回到newbranch继续开发，让两条线都有后续提交，这样对比更明显。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout main",
        "commit",
        "checkout newbranch",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后关键一步：切回main分支，执行cherry-pick把之前那个「Pick me」的commit拿过来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout main",
        "cherry-pick id: \"Pick me\""
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下流程：main先有初始commit，分出newbranch后newbranch做了「Pick me」；main自己也有一个commit；然后newbranch再做一个commit；最后main通过cherry-pick把「Pick me」合并过来。是这个顺序吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "newbranch",
        "cherry-pick"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，完美。这样从下往上看，能清楚看到cherry-pick是从下方的分支把特定提交拿到上方的主分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "bottom-to-top",
        "cherry-pick"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "图已经生成好了，BT方向让main在最上方，newbranch在下方，cherry-pick的箭头从「Pick me」指向main的最新位置，视觉上很清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
